fields.name: Fjord / Accenture Digital
fields.note: We make complex systems simple and elegant. Fjord has been pioneering service design since we opened our doors in 2001. Together with our clients, we’ve created services that make millions of people’s lives a little better every day. We’re human-centered, with an eye on disrupting whole industries. And now, as part of Accenture Interactive, we can broaden our reach even further.

fields.name: İstanbul Studio
fields.note: Turkey is one of the fastest-growing economies in Europe; the communications and consumer electronics sectors are thriving. Fjord’s work with banking giant Garanti and mobile operator Turkcell has positioned us at the heart of this dynamic change.

fields.name: Berlin Studio
fields.note: Fjord Berlin opened in 2007, and was quickly established as one of the city’s most innovative digital agencies. We’re one part spreadsheet, two parts creative plus a sprinkle of storytelling, and in one of Europe’s most dynamic cities the pace of change is faster than ever.

fields.name: Helsinki Studio
fields.note: Fjord Helsinki opened in 2003. With offices in the very centre of the city, we’ve established a formidable reputation as one of the top digital design agencies in the Nordic region.

fields.name: London Studio
fields.note: Fjord London was founded in 2001. The office today employs some of the most experienced and talented digital design specialists in the market, and is working on leading projects for UK and international clients.

fields.name: Madrid Studio
fields.note: Fjord Spain opened in Madrid in late 2009, and since then we’ve been captivating leading brands in Spain and Latin America like Telefonica, BBVA and Globo with our transformative design. We have even been described as the Barcelona FC of the Spanish design industry.

fields.name: New York Studio
fields.note: Fjord New York has been on the scene since 2009, and rapidly established itself the secret weapon of design and innovation for clients like Citibank, ESPN, Harvard Medical School, and Qualcomm. Located in New York’s Flatiron neighborhood, the studio is a foodie’s dream—we’re right next door to the City Bakery and 5th Avenue’s regular line up of local gourmet food trucks.

fields.name: Paris Studio
fields.note: Fjord Paris opened in 2012. Our office is not just located in the heart of the city: we are in fact facing the Conservatoire National d’Arts et Métiers, arguably France’s first-ever design education institution.

fields.name: San Francisco Studio
fields.note: Fjord San Francisco opened its doors in 2011 and has quickly grown to become our West Coast hub for working with the Bay Area’s most innovative companies. Overlooking Union Square in the heart of downtown SF, the studio is home to an eclectic mix of designers, artists, marathon runners, tech nerds, and foodies.

fields.name: Stockholm Studio
fields.note: Fjord Stockholm opened in June 2011 and we are located in the very centre of the city. We totally rock! We do amazing work in the telecoms, media and finance sectors and look forward to meeting you soon!
